{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/yeofr\/yeofrsdk\/begingalleryenrollment(faceid:name:posesequence:lightingphase:)"]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/YEOFRSDK\/beginGalleryEnrollment(faceID:name:poseSequence:lightingPhase:)"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@discardableResult"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"beginGalleryEnrollment","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"faceID","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s5Int64V","text":"Int64","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"name","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"poseSequence"},{"text":": [","kind":"text"},{"text":"PoseTarget","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR10PoseTargetO","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/PoseTarget"},{"text":"] = PoseTarget.defaultGallerySequence, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"lightingPhase","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"LightingPhaseConfig","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR19LightingPhaseConfigV","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/LightingPhaseConfig"},{"text":" = .standard) -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FRSDKReturnCode","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR15FRSDKReturnCodeO","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FRSDKReturnCode"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inline